{"id":"p002","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p002-s0","tokens":[{"s":"『"},{"s":"へぇ"},{"s":"……"},{"s":"格好いい","r":"かっこいい","v":"v2279"},{"s":"じゃん"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"'Heeh... not bad.'"}},{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p002-s1","tokens":[{"s":"クライ","v":"v1735"},{"s":"ちゃん"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"デザイン","v":"v2280"},{"s":"し","v":"v0004","lemma":"する"},{"s":"た"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"？"},{"s":"』"}],"help":{"translation":"'Did you design this, Cry-chan?'","note":"ちゃん attached to a male name from a female speaker is the same affectionate / teasing register Liz used in chapter 1; the speaker here is most likely Liz."}}]}
{"id":"p003","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p003-s0","tokens":[{"s":"『"},{"s":"でも"},{"s":"これ","v":"v1239"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"こんな","v":"v0319"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"被って","r":"かぶって","v":"v0526","lemma":"被る"},{"s":"戦ったら","r":"たたかったら","v":"v0957","lemma":"戦う"},{"s":"絶対","r":"ぜったい","v":"v0545"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"怖がられ","r":"こわがられ","v":"v2281","lemma":"怖がる"},{"s":"ます"},{"s":"よ"},{"s":"ね"},{"s":"……"},{"s":"』"}],"help":{"translation":"'But — fighting in something like this, you'd absolutely scare people...'","note":"怖がられる = passive of 怖がる (\"to be feared\"). The sentence trails off on 〜よね……, the speaker softening the observation rather than pressing it."}}]}
{"id":"p004","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p004-s0","tokens":[{"s":"『"},{"s":"いい","v":"v0851"},{"s":"ん"},{"s":"じゃ"},{"s":"ねー"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"？"}],"help":{"translation":"'Why not?'"}},{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p004-s1","tokens":[{"s":"こんな","v":"v0319"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"なくて"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"どうせ","v":"v0633"},{"s":"すぐ","v":"v0486"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"恐れられる","r":"おそれられる","v":"v1693","lemma":"恐れる"},{"s":"』"}],"help":{"translation":"'They'll fear us soon enough anyway, even without these.'"}}]}
{"id":"p005","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p005-s0","tokens":[{"s":"顔","r":"かお","v":"v0075"},{"s":"全面","r":"ぜんめん","v":"v2201"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"覆う","r":"おおう","v":"v1194"},{"s":"それ"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"被る","r":"かぶる","v":"v0526"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"身体","r":"からだ","v":"v0782"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"大きさ","r":"おおきさ","v":"v1090"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"性別","r":"せいべつ","v":"v2282"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"問わず","r":"とわず","v":"v2283"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"まるで","v":"v0439"},{"s":"怪物","r":"かいぶつ","v":"v1684"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"ように"},{"s":"見えた","r":"みえた","v":"v0173","lemma":"見える"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Once it was on, covering the entire face, body size or gender no longer mattered — you looked like a monster.","note":"〜を問わず = \"regardless of ~,\" a fixed phrase. The sentence frames the mask's anonymising power matter-of-factly."}}]}
{"id":"p006","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p006-s0","tokens":[{"s":"かつて","v":"v0861"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"ある","v":"v0106"},{"s":"田舎","r":"いなか","v":"v2284"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"町","r":"まち","v":"v2285"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"ハンター","v":"v0102"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"憧れる","r":"あこがれる","v":"v0405"},{"s":"六人","r":"ろくにん","v":"v0040"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"子供","r":"こども","v":"v0015"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"いた"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Once upon a time, in a certain country town, there were six children who dreamed of being Hunters."}}]}
{"id":"p007","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p007-s0","tokens":[{"s":"誰","r":"だれ","v":"v0268"},{"s":"より"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"勇敢","r":"ゆうかん","v":"v0046"},{"s":"な"},{"s":"少年","r":"しょうねん","v":"v0688"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"剣","r":"けん","v":"v0951"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"愛し","r":"あいし","v":"v2286","lemma":"愛する"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"無双","r":"むそう","v":"v0136"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"『"},{"s":"剣士","r":"ソードマン","v":"v0137"},{"s":"』"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"目指した","r":"めざした","v":"v0033","lemma":"目指す"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"The bravest of them — a boy — loved his sword, and aimed to become an unmatched 'Swordsman.'"}}]}
{"id":"p008","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p008-s0","tokens":[{"s":"誰","r":"だれ","v":"v0268"},{"s":"より"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"好奇心","r":"こうきしん","v":"v2287"},{"s":"が"},{"s":"強かった","r":"つよかった","v":"v0044","lemma":"強い"},{"s":"少女","r":"しょうじょ","v":"v2288"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"先","r":"さき","v":"v0287"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"求め","r":"もとめ","v":"v0196","lemma":"求める"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"最速","r":"さいそく","v":"v2289"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"『"},{"s":"盗賊","r":"シーフ","v":"v0142"},{"s":"』"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"目指した","r":"めざした","v":"v0033","lemma":"目指す"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"The most curious of them — a girl — sought what lay ahead, and aimed to become the swiftest 'Thief.'"}}]}
{"id":"p009","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p009-s0","tokens":[{"s":"誰","r":"だれ","v":"v0268"},{"s":"より"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"優しかった","r":"やさしかった","v":"v2290","lemma":"優しい"},{"s":"少年","r":"しょうねん","v":"v0688"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"皆","r":"みんな","v":"v2291"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"守る","r":"まもる","v":"v1227"},{"s":"こと"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"望み","r":"のぞみ","v":"v2292","lemma":"望む"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"最高","r":"さいこう","v":"v1121"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"『"},{"s":"守護騎士","r":"パラディン","v":"v0249"},{"s":"』"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"目指した","r":"めざした","v":"v0033","lemma":"目指す"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"The kindest of them — a boy — wished to protect them all, and aimed to become the supreme 'Paladin.'"}}]}
{"id":"p010","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p010-s0","tokens":[{"s":"誰","r":"だれ","v":"v0268"},{"s":"より"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"賢かった","r":"かしこかった","v":"v2293","lemma":"賢い"},{"s":"少女","r":"しょうじょ","v":"v2288"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"その"},{"s":"先見","r":"せんけん","v":"v2294"},{"s":"故","r":"ゆえ","v":"v0421"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"最強","r":"さいきょう","v":"v0036"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"力","r":"ちから","v":"v0088"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"欲し","r":"ほっし","v":"v2295","lemma":"欲する"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"至高","r":"しこう","v":"v2296"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"『"},{"s":"魔導師","r":"マギ","v":"v0237"},{"s":"』"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"目指した","r":"めざした","v":"v0033","lemma":"目指す"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"The wisest of them — a girl — foresaw what was coming and craved the greatest power, aiming to become the ultimate 'Mage.'","note":"先見 = \"foresight,\" literary. 至高の = \"supreme / highest,\" used here as a kind of poetic flourish in a series of similar parallel sentences."}}]}
{"id":"p011","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p011-s0","tokens":[{"s":"誰","r":"だれ","v":"v0268"},{"s":"より"},{"s":"も"},{"s":"弱かった","r":"よわかった","v":"v0351","lemma":"弱い"},{"s":"少女","r":"しょうじょ","v":"v2288"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"自身","r":"じしん","v":"v0942"},{"s":"に"},{"s":"できる","v":"v0121"},{"s":"こと"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"考え","r":"かんがえ","v":"v0927","lemma":"考える"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"最優","r":"さいゆう","v":"v2297"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"『"},{"s":"錬金術師","r":"アルケミスト","v":"v0242"},{"s":"』"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"目指した","r":"めざした","v":"v0033","lemma":"目指す"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"The weakest of them — a girl — thought about what she could do, and aimed to become the finest 'Alchemist.'"}}]}
{"id":"p012","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p012-s0","tokens":[{"s":"いつ","v":"v1541"},{"s":"だって"},{"s":"笑って","r":"わらって","v":"v1161","lemma":"笑う"},{"s":"いた"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"They were always laughing."}}]}
{"id":"p013","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p013-s0","tokens":[{"s":"強さ","r":"つよさ","v":"v2262"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"目指した","r":"めざした","v":"v0033","lemma":"目指す"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"They aimed for strength."}},{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p013-s1","tokens":[{"s":"天稟","r":"てんぴん","v":"v2298"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"努力","r":"どりょく","v":"v0253"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"彼ら","r":"かれら","v":"v0276"},{"s":"を"},{"s":"裏切らなかった","r":"うらぎらなかった","v":"v2299","lemma":"裏切る"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"Talent and effort did not betray them.","note":"天稟 (\"innate aptitude / heaven-given gift\") is a literary word for talent, more elevated than the everyday 才能."}}]}
{"id":"p014","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p014-s0","tokens":[{"s":"『"},{"s":"笑う","r":"わらう","v":"v1161"},{"s":"骸骨","r":"がいこつ","v":"v1645"},{"s":"』"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"ルーク","v":"v0855"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"言葉","r":"ことば","v":"v0290"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"通り","r":"とおり","v":"v0296"},{"s":"、"},{"s":"いつしか","v":"v2300"},{"s":"知る","r":"しる","v":"v0209"},{"s":"人","r":"ひと","v":"v0398"},{"s":"ぞ"},{"s":"知る","r":"しる","v":"v0209"},{"s":"畏怖","r":"いふ","v":"v2301"},{"s":"の"},{"s":"象徴","r":"しょうちょう","v":"v2302"},{"s":"と"},{"s":"なった","v":"v0008","lemma":"なる"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"The 'Laughing Skull,' just as Luke had said, in time became a feared symbol known only to those in the know.","note":"いつしか = \"at some point / before one knew it,\" a bookish adverb. 知る人ぞ知る is an idiom: \"known only to those who know\" — a connoisseur's marker. The ぞ here is a literary emphatic that locks the relative-clause-style construction in place."}}]}
{"id":"p015","sentences":[{"id":"06-nageki-no-bourei-1-p015-s0","tokens":[{"s":"そして","v":"v0149"},{"s":"僕","r":"ぼく","v":"v0074"},{"s":"は"},{"s":"──"},{"s":"。"}],"help":{"translation":"And as for me──.","note":"は──。 ends the sentence on the topic-marker plus dash, deliberately leaving the predicate blank — what \"I\" became is unstated, the silence itself doing the work. A closing-line technique that pivots back to the present-tense narrator from the flashback."}}]}
